info.author: Mosek ApS
info.description:
MOSEK is a package for large-scale convex and mixed-integer optimization, including LP, QP, SOCP, exponential and power cone problems, SDP, QCQP and MIP.

Documentation and examples can be found at the [MOSEK website](https://www.mosek.com)

MOSEK requires a license. Free of charge trial licenses as well as licenses for non-commercial academic use can be obtained from the [MOSEK website](https://www.mosek.com).
